// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/4csyDX three points circle, 2024 by jt

// Implementation of a circle through three points as described in
// https://math.stackexchange.com/questions/213658/get-the-equation-of-a-circle-when-given-3-points
// https://web.archive.org/web/20161011113446/http://www.abecedarical.com/zenosamples/zs_circle3pts.html

// 3d variant: https://www.shadertoy.com/view/lffyDs four points sphere

// tags: circle, 3, three, points, point

